If someone has violated the copyrights, you can write to me and I delete my map. The T 2 maps and 24 places in CT. A map of the terrorists shot gun to police. The road on which the police simply going to break out puzzle. The map is all that the police should get to the very top of course. Then, defeat the terrorists.

Objective:

T's have to get from one side of the map to the other only using smoke grenades while Ct's have scout snipers and have to try and kill them before they get to the end.

At the end of the map there are AWP snipers that can be used to shoot the CT's or a button which blows them all up xD

there are a few weapons spread out along the map but are very dangerous to get to but if you do manage to gain one it can be annoying for the CT's.

There are 6 Ct spawns and 30 T spawns so there is en equal balance on teams if you have a full enough server.

Enjoy :D

MG_RUN_FETBOY_RUN ----------------------------- The aim of this map is for the Terrorists to run around 4 stages of the map trying to dodge the smash blocks that fly out of the cannons which 4 CT's control! The stages get more difficult as time goes on, if the T's do manage to make it to the end of the map then they will be able to kill the CT's unless they got shot over the top by the cannons ^^. Each stage has a time limit on to make it to the end: *STAGE 1* = 1 Minute *STAGE 2* = 50 Seconds *STAGE 3* = 1 Minute *STAGE 4* = Unlimited Time. Map Requires mp_limitteams 0 server setting. *IMPORTANT NOTE ABOUT PLAYER SLOTS* This map is 20 slots so that there is an even amount of T's on each side. If you would like a map with 32+ slots then send me a FPSB private message and I will send you it. You can find my prefab cannon here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/3354 Thanks Paul_Deagle (aka [SG] Paul)

mg_runaway_v1

It is a small mini game map, both teams start without a weapon.
The ground consists of many fields. If you step on them they go down.
After a time they will come up again.
There are special fields where you can stay longer, but after some seconds they will be closed for a long time.
In the middle of the map is a mp5. But you can not take it.
After a while players get damage every second and it will be possible to take the mp5 from the middle of the map. So for example if there are only two players left and nobody wins, the faster one gets the mp5.

I would be happy if you post your feedback.

Thank you very much,

MG ROTA DERP V1_1

This map was created for Gamebanana's Twisted Reality contest.

The key features are the following:

  • 64 player spawn
  • cubemaps
  • custom made particles
  • custom made sounds and soundscapes
  • custom made animated models
  • 8 portals leading to different areas + a final stage
  • checkpoints
  • a boss with dynamic movement, health and attacks. Including a HP meter with more/less HP depending on the amount of players present

V1_1

  • fixed the crash in the fetus area
  • doubled the HP of the boss

I hope that my work will result in your enjoyment, have a good one and i'll see you ingame. Best regards! ;)

Do not edit and/or reupload this map, do not copy parts from this map without asking either. Feel free to decompile the map to look at how things were done though.

Any questions, bugs or suggestions? Send them to Pellevoice@gmail.com
